2DA V1.0
*
     RESOURCE
0    0x6000
1    avprefr
2    avprefg
3    avprefc

# Contains the scheme of the avatar animation IDs based on character stats.
# The first row contains the base animation ID.
# A second column in the first row may store the first stance of the generated character.
# Additional rows contain tables which additively modify the ID based on a stat.
